description.et:
More detailed instructions for homework are given in the lecture:
- independent work is designed according to the instructions;
- the homework and practicl excercises are written, presented orally or visually;
- the author's text is a logical, meaningful and original written work (1 page of A4), submitted in time before each lecture and seminar (10 in total);
- in agreement with the lecturer, the homework may also be submitted as a group work.
- the oral presentation and discussion of the written final work takes place in a colloquium. The lecturer has the right to change the plan according to the needs of the participants/students.
